name: Value Startup
overview:
We are unconventional company!

We are driven by the essence and spirits of the upcoming and aspiring leaders and entrepreneurs.

Founded by serials entrepreneurs who are specialized in getting the job done. Empowering leaders and entrepreneurs to lead their companies and businesses to new heights.

If you are looking for a theoretically dense content, developed by theoretically based company by theoretically driven founders. We honestly assure you that we are not your best pick!

If you are looking for a group of people who are challenging the conventional, bending the rules. A group who successfully done what they preach. Then stick with us, we guarantee you would find what you need.

Besides Business Training and Coaching we offer Lead Generation Service as well as Product Launch Management. We only accepted business opportunities if we believe we can add considerable added value to your business growth and development.

This is why we are the only coaching firm who occasionally apologize to take on new business opportunities. Ensuring the added value is a must.

Hence this is why we are the only firm who is so confident of its services that we offer a money back guarantee if for any reason what so ever we didn’t deliver to your expectations.
